*'''EnGenius EMP-8602 PLUS-S''' :- High 600mW wireless power :- Up to 150mW for 802.11a / 600mW for 802.11b/g :- 802.11a/b/g Dual Band Support (4.9GHz support) :- Provides 2.4GHz or 5GHz wireless frequency :- Operates in 5GHz band to avoid interference from 802.11b/g work devices :- 802.11a offers more wireless channels than 802.11b/g :- Intelligent quality of service (QoS) technology :- Ensures robust signal to overe long distances :- Offers superior WiFi coverage over leading brands :- Support 802.11e standard for wireless multimedia enhancements
